{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.320", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.440", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.560", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.600", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was das Leben der Menschen und die Arbeitszeit betrifft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.280", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so versucht der Gesetzgeber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.640", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Arbeitsleben in einer gewissen Flexibilit\u00e4t zu regeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.800", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auf der einen Seite haben die Mitarbeiter oft den Wunsch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.760", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihre Arbeitszeit flexibel zu gestalten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.160", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auf der anderen Seite gibt es nat\u00fcrlich auch den Wunsch bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.680", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Begehren des Arbeitgebers nach einer bestimmten Flexibilit\u00e4t,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.480", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gleichzeitig aber auch nach geordneten Betriebsabl\u00e4ufen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.040", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beides gilt es hier in Einklang zu bringen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.160", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bevor man gesetzgeberisch t\u00e4tig wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.480", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist es eigentlich am besten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.680", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sich diejenigen dar\u00fcber unterhalten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.520", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die tats\u00e4chlich daf\u00fcr zust\u00e4ndig sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.920", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich die Arbeitsvertragsparteien und die Tarifparteien, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.040", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die hier auch gewisse Gestaltungsm\u00f6glichkeiten haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.520", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man muss sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.560", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In den allermeisten F\u00e4llen klappt das in Deutschland sehr gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.760", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und es gelingt sehr gut."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.840", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Gestaltung hat allerdings auch eine gewisse Grenze, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.680", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar dort, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.840", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo man an die Grenze der Machbarkeit kommt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.240", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da muss man dann zun\u00e4chst einmal den Unternehmer fragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.480", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "inwieweit es m\u00f6glich ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.720", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auf Flexibilisierungsw\u00fcnsche der Mitarbeiter einzugehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.440", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch hier sind die Interessen der geordneten Betriebsabl\u00e4ufe zu beachten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.880", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Arbeitsrecht sieht aktuell entsprechende M\u00f6glichkeiten und Grenzen vor. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.640", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich darf an dieser Stelle das Arbeitszeitgesetz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.400", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Teilzeit- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.320", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Befristungsgesetz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.120", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber auch das Mindestlohngesetz nennen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.880", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Vorschl\u00e4ge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.360", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sie unterbreiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.760", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen der Fraktion der Linken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.880", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00f6rdern das gerade Gesagte sicherlich nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.240", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielmehr schr\u00e4nken Sie die notwendige Freiheit der Unternehmer ein und"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.760", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ebenso die gew\u00fcnschten Freiheiten der Arbeitnehmer; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.680", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Einzelnen komme ich gleich dazu."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.080", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der erste Punkt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.720", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Sie fordern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.880", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.640", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die w\u00f6chentliche H\u00f6chstarbeitszeit von 48 auf 40\u00a0Stunden zu reduzieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.800", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei \u00fcbersehen Sie allerdings, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.400", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es auch unter Arbeitnehmern den Wunsch gibt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.480", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie werden es nicht glauben\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.760", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mehr als die 40\u00a0Stunden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.200", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die von Ihnen angesetzt worden sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.400", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu arbeiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.520", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Warum? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.800", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Weil sie sich aufgrund ihrer Mehrarbeit etwas leisten m\u00f6chten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.760", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sprechen von einer Umverteilung der Arbeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.320", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlich willkommen in der Planwirtschaft! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.120", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es sollte Ihnen doch wohl bekannt sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.160", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es bisher noch nie funktioniert hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.880", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wohlstand und Prosperit\u00e4t so voranzubringen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.040", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch den Menschen ist damit nicht gedient. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.920", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier k\u00f6nnen wir uns die eigene Geschichte anschauen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.880", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen auch betrachten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.440", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir zurzeit einen Fachkr\u00e4ftemangel zu verzeichnen haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.320", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Unternehmen leiden sehr darunter. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.240", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Sie dann noch sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.800", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eWir wollen die Arbeitszeiten reduzieren\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.280", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist das sicherlich nicht im Interesse der Leistungsf\u00e4higkeit unserer Wirtschaft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.280", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und wenn das dazu f\u00fchrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.320", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Steuereinnahmen nicht mehr in dem Umfang sprudeln wie bisher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.680", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann ist das sicherlich auch nicht im Interesse aller. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.720", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Auswirkungen brauche ich hier nicht n\u00e4her zu schildern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.880", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Ihrer Begr\u00fcndung sprechen Sie aber nicht nur von einer Umverteilung der Arbeit allgemein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.680", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch von einer Umverteilung unbezahlter Arbeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.120", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Deutschland ist nach dem geltenden Arbeitsrecht jede Arbeitsstunde zu verg\u00fcten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.840", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00e4llt eine \u00dcberstunde an, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.360", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist diese entweder zu verg\u00fcten oder in Freizeit auszugleichen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.600", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Geschieht das nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.800", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann ist das bereits jetzt rechtswidrig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.440", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Rechtsweg steht jedem offen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.680", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jeder kann diesen einschlagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.600", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um zu seinem Recht zu kommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.600", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.200", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "erlauben Sie eine Zwischenfrage oder Zwischenbemerkung der Kollegin Krellmann?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.760", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerne."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.320", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Krellmann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.040", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bitte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.880", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.960", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.480", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Oellers: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.960", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bin im Westen geboren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.160", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie m\u00fcssen mir nicht st\u00e4ndig irgendetwas vorwerfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.520", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was nicht dort passiert ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.280", 
   "id": "s000091", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo ich gelebt und gearbeitet habe. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "281.360", 
   "id": "s000092", 
